lead_paragraph: Manager Claudio Ranieri is confident that nerves will not derail Leicester City's season, after watching his team defeat Watford 1-0 to stretch their lead at the top of the Premier League table.

headline.print_headline: Ranieri Backs Over-Achieving Foxes to Stay Calm on Run In
